{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the next thing, we-- I was called out again, but alone and had to work outside, outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I, I tell you one incident before that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also alone, I was taken and we were-- we already knew what it-- the work was going to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A train has arrived with building material, and we were called then to unload bricks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some people are already were on the wagons and loaded five bricks onto the shoulders of everybody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to run like a marathon about a kilometer on-- onwards to a certain spot where you had to put down the bricks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I never reached that far because although there were every 50 or 100 yards somebody with whips-- and I'm not sure if they were Germans or they were Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't quite look at the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the word schnell, schnell--- quick, on the double, fast-- was eventually picked up by the Ukrainians very quickly and sounded like the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they whipped preferably those with loads, and so they had to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was a little hill, and I went up that hill and down the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "While I was going down the other side, I couldn't be seen from the back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the front, that next guard just whipped somebody, so he wouldn't just see me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was busy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I shed my load, threw it down, and went back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was always thinking running-- if I had to run, it's better without a load than with a load.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I reached the wagon again I tried to get up onto the wagon because I thought loading it onto others is easier than carrying it yourself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
